xWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=0dadab98\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.legco.gov.hk/yr71-72/h720105.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n而該規例, 正正就係根據香港法例第241章緊急情況規例條例所建立. [法例--&gt;規例]<br />\n<br />\n根據網上留言,有人話當年香港貨幣匯率突然急速變差, 所以港督勒令1971年12月20日放假一天, 不過我google搵唔到, 當時我又未出世, 全能連登仔可以問下老豆老母查證<br />\n<br />\n如果當年可以因為貨幣匯率轉差而勒令放假, 我覺得尋日更加合情合理放假, 但林鄭就on99視而不見, 講到國際性會議係最重要, 香港市民安全福利係最後<br />\n<br />\n而家香港政府, 正正就係無才無能兼無德既表表者"},{"pid":"3a0af18db4d8c405b3f0b2348076d5ed1982b9af","tid":825966,"uid":22889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"077fe6145deedc9e5b50665a4aa3ce7d2896332b","tid":825966,"uid":139720,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:21:48.000Z","msg":"林鄭真係好撚柒煩<br />\n縮番埋禮賓府咪撚出聲當幫忙啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:30:31.000Z","msg":"其實佢鳩縮幾日善忘既香港人就唔撚記得㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係要出嚟死雞撐飯蓋 煩膠女人"},{"pid":"3a7cac7e2098adf0ad86164f78d13c6b0fa9a90f","tid":825966,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:31:35.000Z","msg":"明明市民屌緊佢, 佢話佢地好配合係咩玩法 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d19459e55f626b19dfcbeea173f7c8dcb999864c","tid":825966,"uid":91931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:33:37.000Z","msg":"笑撚死我佢同香港人都痴鳩線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"581f60538ed66a123c527b1319b590f6e9133b03","tid":825966,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:34:37.000Z","msg":"佢坐車返工 睇著班市民跨哂欄，行返工好撚開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d404e12f1682283d3883faed306c13623b94f322","tid":825966,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"121e70d918250b47ff6e30549859bcc148db58ab","tid":825966,"uid":37757,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:20:50.000Z","msg":"姐係下次死人冧樓 只要個風除左就都要照返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":